_sText:
Sorry guys for not releasing a map in awhile. This map was put on delay because i had no idea on how to get one panel to stay up at the end. So i just said, screw it, Ill upload it anyway. So sorry guys for the 99% done map.

OBJECTIVE: Stay up as long can without falling.

When the glass turns purple, you better get off that panel. You have 3 seconds before it breaks and you fall to your death.

That is basically it.

-keto
